+## Code Review Report: CartView.jsx
+
+### Summary
+Reviewed `pages/PublicMenu/CartView.jsx` against the scoped CV-B2-B Fix 2-6 requirements from the external task prompt. The current file is an older 1115-line variant and is missing all five scoped fixes.
+
+### High Priority (P1) — Should Fix
+- [P1] Cancelled orders still count toward table and guest totals. `tableOrdersTotal` at `CartView.jsx:514-522` sums all other guests' orders, and `guestTotal` at `CartView.jsx:865` also includes cancelled orders. The file has no `isCancelledOrder` helper yet, so monetary totals remain inflated.
+- [P1] Pending/unconfirmed orders are not modeled. `statusBuckets` at `CartView.jsx:456-466` still exposes only `served` and `in_progress`, there are no pending-specific checks, and `bucketOrder` at `CartView.jsx:1005` still renders only those two buckets. Orders in B44 status `new` cannot appear in the required pending section.
+- [P1] The terminal “Ничего не ждёте” screen is not durable. The V8 branch at `CartView.jsx:928-998` has no `terminalStateShownForVersion`, `terminalVersion`, or localStorage persistence, so it resets after reload instead of staying visible for the current terminal state version.
+
+### Medium Priority (P2) — Recommended
